                    <span>It is a good source to take a glimpse of the history of PC industry to year 1995. It briefly introduced how the major players like Apple, Microsoft, and IBM being involved in the PC industry.  There are a number of participants in this DVD talked about their stories. However, the introduction of those participants is too fast and I find it is hard to follow. Overall, I think it is a good documentary and quite interesting.</span>
                  
              
